      "model_answer": "根据提供的源码片段和上下文，以下是关于 FastAPI 中 `get` 方法的详细分析：\n\n## 基本信息\n\n- **类**: `FastAPI` 类的方法\n- **文件**: `fastapi/applications.py`\n- **行号**: 大约在第 1000 行左右（具体行号可能因版本略有不同）\n\n## 参数列表\n\n```python\ndef get(\n    self,\n    path: Annotated[str, Doc(\"The URL path to be used for this *path operation*.\")],\n    *,\n    response_model: Annotated[Any, Doc(...)] = Default(None),\n    status_code: Annotated[Optional[int], Doc(...)] = None,\n    tags: Annotated[Optional[List[Union[str, Enum]]], Doc(...)] = None,\n    dependencies: Annotated[Optional[Sequence[Depends]], Doc(...)] = None,\n    summary: Annotated[Optional[str], Doc(...)] = None,\n    description: Annotated[Optional[str], Doc(...)] = None,\n    response_description: Annotated[str, Doc(...)] = \"Successful Response\",\n    responses: Annotated[Optional[Dict[Union[int, str], Dict[str, Any]]], Doc(...)] = None,\n    deprecated: Annotated[Optional[bool], Doc(...)] = None,\n    operation_id: Annotated[Optional[str], Doc(...)] = None,\n    response_model_include: Annotated[Optional[IncEx], Doc(...)] = None,\n    response_model_exclude: Annotated[Optional[IncEx], Doc(...)] = None,\n    response_model_by_alias: Annotated[bool, Doc(...)] = True,\n    response_model_exclude_unset: Annotated[bool, Doc(...)] = False,\n    response_model_exclude_defaults: Annotated[bool, Doc(...)] = False,\n    response_model_exclude_none: Annotated[bool, Doc(...)] = False,\n    include_in_schema: Annotated[bool, Doc(...)] = True,\n    response_class: Union[Type[Response], DefaultPlaceholder] = Default(JSONResponse),\n    name: Annotated[Optional[str], Doc(...)] = None,\n    openapi_extra: Annotated[Optional[Dict[str, Any]], Doc(...)] = None,\n    generate_unique_id_function: Callable[[routing.APIRoute], str] = Default(generate_unique_id),\n) -> Callable[[DecoratedCallable], DecoratedCallable]:\n```\n\n## 主要职责\n\n`get` 方法是一个**装饰器**，用于注册 HTTP GET 路径操作。它的主要职责包括：\n\n1. **路径注册**：将指定的 URL 路径与 HTTP GET 方法关联起来\n2. **配置传递**：接收并传递各种路径操作配置参数（如响应模型、状态码、标签、依赖项等）\n3. **委托处理**：最终调用 `self.router.add_api_route()` 方法，将路径操作注册到内部的路由器（`APIRouter`）中\n4. **返回装饰器**：返回一个装饰器函数，该函数接收用户定义的路径操作函数，并将其注册到路由器中\n\n## 函数调用链\n\n```\nFastAPI.get()\n    └── self.router.add_api_route()  # 委托给 APIRouter 的 add_api_route 方法\n        └── 内部路由注册逻辑\n```\n\n## 关键特点\n\n- `get` 方法是一个**装饰器**，通常用于 `@app.get(\"/path\")` 语法\n- 它通过 `*` 参数分隔符强制使用关键字参数（除了 `path` 参数）\n- 所有参数都有详细的文档字符串（通过 `Doc` 类型注解）\n- 最终注册是通过 `self.router`（一个 `APIRouter` 实例）完成的，这体现了 FastAPI 的模块化设计",
