ons()  (fastapi/routing.py)\n            └── APIRouter.add_api_route()  (fastapi/routing.py)\n                └── APIRoute.__init__()  (fastapi/routing.py)\n                    └── 注册到路由表\n```\n\n## 使用示例\n\n```python\nfrom fastapi import FastAPI\n\napp = FastAPI()\n\n@app.options(\"/items/\")\ndef get_item_options():\n    return {\"additions\": [\"Aji\", \"Guacamole\"]}\n```\n\n这个装饰器会注册一个处理 `/items/` 路径的 OPTIONS 请求的路径操作函数。",
